snippet.title: "Hatsune Miku Logic Paint S" Introduction
snippet.description:
"Hatsune Miku Logic Paint S" comes to the Nintendo Switch! 
"Hatsune Miku Logic Paint -MIKULOGI-" has evolved! Now you can play "Hatsune Miku Logic Paint S" on the Nintendo Switch! 
Enjoy "Hatsune Miku Logic Paint S" on the go, at home on the big screen, wherever and whenever with Hatsune Miku and friends! 

■Title: Hatsune Miku Logic Paint S
■Release date: March 18th, 2021 (Thursday)
■Genre: Puzzle
■Supported hardware: Nintendo Switch
■Number of players: 1
■Suggested retail price: 1,500 yen
■Purchasing method: Nintendo eShop (download-only software)
■Twitter：https://twitter.com/cfm_mobile
